{
  "stem": "9601.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Germans, when they were going east [NON-ENGLISH] marching to the east, some of them used to come into the village, you know, look for chickens, you know, fruits and vegetables-- mostly fruits and vegetables they wanted because the army probably didn't provide them.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the kids used to send the-- the Germans to, you know, point out to me that [NON-ENGLISH], a Jew.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of them used to say to the kids, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kill him.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they didn't understand German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But Yiddish-- what we spoke at home-- is a derivative from German, so I taught [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That meant 'kill him,' so the kids said, what he says?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He told us to go home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oy, he says, you know, that's not true.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What did he say?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, he told us to go home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we gathered up and we went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My friends, we went home together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So it's already things began to cook.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then, you know, every generation replaces-- replaces itself, right?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Those politically active people that the Russians did not released during the war, when Germany invaded, they were replaced by other people-- by other college students.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Those were the-- I've concluded on my own that those were the-- the troublemakers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Those were-- those were the people that made life for us miserable.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I'm not saying that their parents were any better, but their parents were more humane-- more understanding what life, what human beings are.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Young people are only interested instant gratification.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I think they were indoctrinated, you know, by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't know this was done that, you know, you've got to clean out the Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That it's OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You have our permission to kill it, because the German policy was anyway then, right?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So they gave them their OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
